# localcosmos-cordova-builder
required environment variable: LOCALCOSMOS_CORDOVA_BUILDER_WORKDIR

using python3 virtualenv
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

add

export LOCALCOSMOS_CORDOVA_BUILDER_WORKDIR=/path/to/workdir

to venv/bin/activate


